                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9740" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1463</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">898 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科创板首例A控A：器械一哥重金“迈瑞”惠泰医疗</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SSE STAR Market&#39;s first case of Public-to-Public M&amp;A: device a brother of the heavy ‘Marry’ APT Medical</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李金茹，王宇豪，王梓沅，赵子怡，李冉，魏嘉希</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳迈瑞生物医疗电子股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科创板；A控A；迈瑞医疗；现金并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SSE STAR Market; A-control A; Mindray Medical; cash acquisition</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">迈瑞医疗是国内医疗器械行业的龙头企业。2024年1月28日，迈瑞医疗宣布通过“协议受让+原实控人放弃表决权”的方式，以66.5亿元人民币现金收购惠泰医疗控制权，该笔交易是科创板首例A控A事件。惠泰医疗是一家专注于心血管领域创新产品研发的企业，其核心产品包括高端医疗器械与智能化解决方案。并购后，迈瑞医疗获得了惠泰医疗的专利技术、研发团队和优质的市场渠道，增强了自身在心血管领域的产品线深度，为实现迈向全球医疗器械前二十的战略目标增添助力。本案例以被并购方的公开市场状况为切入点，从支付方式、并购动因等视角描述此次并购的全景。通过案例讨论，引导学员思考被并购方公开市场状况对并购的影响，现金并购的合理性，A控A的动因及绩效，以此为其他上市公司在选择被并购方时提供参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Mindray Medical is a leading enterprise in the domestic medical device industry. 28 January 2024, Mindray Medical announced to acquire the control of APT medical with 6.65 billion RMB in cash by the way of ‘agreement to be transferred + the original real controller to give up the voting right’, the transaction is the first case of SSE STAR Market&#39;s A-control A event. APT medical is an enterprise focusing on the research and development of innovative products in the cardiovascular field, and its core products include high-end medical devices and intelligent solutions. After the merger and acquisition, Mindray Medical acquired APT medical&#39;s patented technology, R&amp;D team and high-quality market channels, which enhanced the depth of its own product line in the cardiovascular field and added help to achieve the strategic goal of moving towards the top 20 of global medical devices. The case takes the open market situation of the acquired party as the starting point, and describes the panorama of the merger from the perspectives of payment method and motivation of the merger. Through the case discussion, the participants are guided to think about the impact of the open market status of the acquiree on M&amp;A, the risk of cash M&amp;A, and the motivation and performance of A-control A, so as to provide references for other listed companies in choosing the acquiree.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》《财务会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购动因、并购方式、并购的支付方式、并购估值</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-08</td>
                            </tr>
